7. User Stories
Customer Stories
•	As a Customer, I want to sign up using my phone number and OTP, so I can access the app quickly without a password.
•	As a Customer, I want to save my car details (e.g., Honda Civic, 2019), so I don’t need to re-enter them for each booking.
•	As a Customer, I want to browse services with transparent pricing (e.g., Oil Change: PKR 5,000), so I can budget effectively.
•	As a Customer, I want to book a mechanic to my location, so I avoid visiting a workshop.
•	As a Customer, I want to track my mechanic’s location on a map, so I know when they’ll arrive.
•	As a Customer, I want to pay via JazzCash, so I can avoid cash transactions.
•	As a Customer, I want to rate my mechanic and leave feedback, so I can help improve service quality.
Mechanic Stories
•	As a Mechanic, I want to register with my certifications, so customers trust my expertise.
•	As a Mechanic, I want to toggle my availability, so I can manage my schedule.
•	As a Mechanic, I want to receive job alerts for nearby bookings, so I can maximize earnings.
•	As a Mechanic, I want in-app navigation to the customer’s location, so I arrive on time.
•	As a Mechanic, I want to mark jobs as completed, so I get paid promptly.
Admin Stories
•	As an Admin, I want to monitor real-time bookings, so I can balance mechanic assignments.
•	As an Admin, I want to verify mechanic certifications, so only qualified professionals are onboarded.
•	As an Admin, I want to generate reports (e.g., revenue, top services), so I can make data-driven decisions.
